text: Frédérique Heligon (born 27 February 1970) is a French rower. She competed in the women's coxless four event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:French female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of France Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Nantes
